mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector.query.row

Class RowProviderSkippingIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector.query.row.RowProviderSkippingIterator

  • public class RowProviderSkippingIterator
extends Object
    This class wraps a source iterator and a row provider to provide the logic for seeks based on the given row provider to the given source iterator. It is dependent on seek calls delegated to it from a parent Iterator.
